## AlertManager

Test SMTP
```
curl -XPOST http://<ALERTMANAGER_SERVICE>:9093/api/v2/alerts \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '[{
    "labels": {
      "alertname": "SMTPTest",
      "severity": "critical",
      "namespace": "monitoring"
    },
    "annotations": {
      "summary": "Manual SMTP test",
      "description": "Testing Alertmanager email delivery"
    }
  }]'
```
